{
  "stem": "6195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't tell him that I had the [NON-ENGLISH] anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I said, but my brother, who is the manager, is here too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Without him, we-- I can't do anything, because he makes the machines going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I went to the-- to my brother, which was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a fair run, but I was running.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I wasn't walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I said, you say that we are working.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he said to me, I'm not going to lie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I said, for heaven's sake, who are you cheating?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I am not a liar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Come with me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So in order not to put my brother in that situation that he-- he wouldn't lie.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He just wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So when he asked him, what do you do there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I said, as I said, he is the manager.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He said to that Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he said, take them back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I said, what about my sister?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She works there too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She's only very young, but she works.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it's a small staff there, because the [NON-ENGLISH] doesn't want to employ more people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So we have to do with whatever we can-- work hard and-- so that the Luftwaffe can operate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "How many bloody Jews is still left in your family?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I said, none.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "What happened to them?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Oh, well, we were sort of orphans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because you can't say the Ger-- Nazis have killed her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "When we walked back, my brother said to me, if I wouldn't know you, I would have thought that you are a born liar.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I said, for heaven's sake.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Your life is at stake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You don't-- you cheat your enemy.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
